description:
Creamy Coconut Mushroom Vegan Pizza! Get the full recipe here: http://bit.ly/VeganPizzaCoconutMushroom

This coconut mushroom cheeseless pizza is so rich and creamy everyone will love it. The white pizza sauce is made from coconut milk, thyme, and lemon and it cooks down in the oven to a rich creamy layer. The mushrooms are sautéd before adding them for perfect vegan pizza toppings. Mushroom lovers rejoice! A rich pizza vegans will love and so will everyone else too.
name: Vegan Pizza • Creamy Coconut Mushroom
